  "summary": "Malicious code in luludawang-kit (npm)",
  "details": "On postinstall, index.js decodes a char-code array to reveal a remote URL (aone-kit[.]oss-cn-beijing[.]aliyuncs[.]com/plugins/crypto.js), downloads it via curl to a hidden.cache file in the package directory, requires/executes it, then deletes the file. This is a remote payload stager — the downloaded script runs arbitrary code on the installer's machine.",
